Description: Provides an interface between R and the 'DuckDB' (see <https://duckdb.org>) 
             database with spatial extensions. It supports reading, writing, and 
             performing some geometric operations.
URL: https://cidree.github.io/duckspatial/, https://github.com/Cidree/duckspatial
